m'hot nit gelozn nit aher un nit ahin.

345
00:15:19,795 --> 00:15:22,422
heyst dos ayer familye iz gegangen ale in di groyse ge-

346
00:15:21,972 --> 00:15:23,435
ale in di groyse geto.

347
00:15:24,352 --> 00:15:26,995
yetst volt ikh aykh gevolt fregn nokh a frage.

348
00:15:27,204 --> 00:15:29,580
ven ir flegt geyn arbetn als malekh

