⟨nor⟩ vos hot ir gearbet faktish?

352
00:15:31,574 --> 00:15:32,440
ikh?

353
00:15:32,440 --> 00:15:34,353
ikh hob gearbet oyfn erodrom.

354
00:15:37,784 --> 00:15:38,656
UNK

355
00:15:39,927 --> 00:15:43,162
mir hobn, mir hobn geshm- ⟨fregt⟩ vos ikh hob gearbet.

