flegn zey lozn nemen.

379
00:16:41,875 --> 00:16:44,013
fislekh mit keplekh.

380
00:16:44,289 --> 00:16:46,674
di fislekh mit di keplekh flegn zey arophakn.

381
00:16:46,685 --> 00:16:48,046
dos hot men gekent nemen.

382
00:16:48,102 --> 00:16:51,472
