408
00:17:53,397 --> 00:17:56,305
hot men gemuzt lozn biz ⟨m'hot undz⟩ aroyfgefirt oyf PETROVKA.

409
00:17:56,497 --> 00:17:58,179
mir zaynen shoyn avek on pek.

410
00:17:58,657 --> 00:18:01,807
⟨tsi⟩ zey hobn gevelt tsunemen di zakhn, vos ⟨mit⟩ zey hobn gedarft hobn

