413
00:18:07,364 --> 00:18:09,687
mir zaynen gekumen in geto azoy vi mir hobn

414
00:18:09,811 --> 00:18:11,901
mir zaynen gekumen dos vos iz geblibn in shtub.

415
00:18:11,901 --> 00:18:13,164
dos vos iz geblibn.

416
00:18:14,401 --> 00:18:16,319
mir hobn nit gehat keyn meglekhkeytn.

417
00:18:16,780 --> 00:18:17,973
nor vos?

